                  <span class="text-[10px] text-primary-700 bg-white border border-primary-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Méthode</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-300 text-[10px]">›</span>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-primary-700 bg-white border border-primary-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">À propos</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-300 text-[10px]">›</span>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-primary-700 bg-white border border-primary-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">Témoignages</span>
                  <span class="text-neutral-300 text-[10px]">›</span>
                  <span class="text-[10px] bg-green-600 text-white px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-medium ml-0.5">Email</span>
